WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Wildlife surveys use mathematics to protect animals!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
We count species, measure habitats, and track population changes.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Data collection helps us understand mountain ecosystems.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Every number contributes to conservation efforts.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Mathematics helps us care for alpine wildlife!